
The OPERA Team would gratefully like to acknowledge contributions to the OPERA pipeline.

- The thorium argon atlas thar_MM201006.dat was adopted from and can be found at 
http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/~mmurphy/thar/index.html as published in Astrophysics:

"Selection of ThAr lines for wavelength calibration of echelle spectra and implications 
for variations in the fine-structure constant"
M. T. Murphy (1), P. Tzanavaris (2,3), J. K. Webb (2), C. Lovis (4) 
(1) Institute of Astronomy, Cambridge, UK; (
(2) University of New South Wales, Sydney, Australia; 
(3) Institute of Astronomy and Astrophysics, National Observatory of Athens, Greece; 
(4) Observatoire de Geneve, Switzerland)
(http://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0703623)

